
v0.2.0:
 - introduced hLink
 - implemented resuming downloads
 - fix konami code easter egg not working
 - fix bug where single line panic message wouldn't show
 - add find missing dlc/updates feature
 - add translations
 - add proxy support
 - add sprites for battery
